OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy across Scotland,
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland and parts of northern
OL,7,FEngland, with rain at times, heaviest
OL,8,Fin western Scotland. Elsewhere, plenty
OL,9,Fof hazy sunshine after early cloud
OL,10,Fclears. Warm or very warm for many.
OL,11,FLocally hot in south-eastern England.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FFine, warm and mostly clear
OL,14,Fin the south, though cloud thickens
OL,15,Facross Wales and the southwest with
OL,16,Fsome fog. Cloudy further north with
OL,17,Frain, heaviest in western and
OL,18,Fnorthwestern Scotland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
