OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FRain persists across northern
OL,6,Fand northwestern Scotland. Cloudy at
OL,7,Ffirst across Northern Ireland and
OL,8,Fnorthern England with patchy drizzle.
OL,9,FElsewhere, sunny spells. Very warm and
OL,10,Flocally hot in the southeast.
